---
import { getLangFromUrl } from "src/i18n/utils";

const lang = getLangFromUrl(Astro.url);

const faqs = {
  en: {
    title: "Frequently Asked Questions",
    questions: [
    {
      id: "1",
      title: "How does Moda Link operate as an online store?",
      description:
        "Moda link does not directly sell products or handle orders. We are an affiliate platform that curates the most outstanding clothing on the market. When you click on a product, you will be redirected to the corresponding affiliate's purchase page.",
    },
    {
      id: "2",
      title: "Do you handle shipping or product logistics?",
      description:
        "We do not handle shipping or manage product logistics. Our main function is to present you with the best clothing options available through affiliate links, streamlining your shopping experience.",
    },
    {
      id: "3",
      title: "How can I purchase the products I see on Moda Link?",
      description:
        "To purchase a product you're interested in, simply click on the corresponding link. This will take you directly to the affiliate's detail and purchase page, where you can complete the transaction according to their terms and conditions.",
    },
    {
      id: "4",
      title: "Which brands or companies are associated with Moda Link?",
      description:
        "We collaborate with various brands and companies through affiliate programs. When you click on a product, you can learn more about the brand and make a direct purchase from their website.",
    },
    {
      id: "5",
      title: "How can I trust the quality of the recommended products?",
      description:
        "We strive to select quality products from reputable brands. However, the quality guarantee and after-sales service depend on the affiliate. We recommend reviewing the policies of each company before making a purchase.",
    },
    {
      id: "6",
      title: "Do you have any return or refund policies?",
      description:
        "We do not manage return or refund processes, as transactions are conducted directly with the affiliates. Be sure to review the return policies of the affiliated company before making a purchase.",
    },
  ]
  },
  es: {
    title: "Preguntas frecuentes",
    questions: [
    {
      id: "1",
      title: "¿Cómo opera Moda link como tienda online?",
      description:
        "Moda link no vende directamente productos ni gestiona pedidos. Somos una plataforma de afiliados que recopila las prendas más destacadas del mercado. Al hacer clic en un producto, serás redirigido a la página de compra del afiliado correspondiente.",
    },
    {
      id: "2",
      title: "¿Realizan envíos o manejan logística de productos?",
      description:
        "No realizamos envíos ni gestionamos la logística de los productos. Nuestra función principal es presentarte las mejores opciones de ropa disponibles a través de enlaces de afiliados, facilitándote la experiencia de compra.",
    },
    {
      id: "3",
      title: "¿Cómo puedo comprar los productos que veo en Moda link?",
      description:
        "Para adquirir un producto que te interese, simplemente haz clic en el enlace correspondiente. Esto te llevará directamente a la página de detalle y compra del afiliado, donde podrás realizar la transacción de acuerdo con sus términos y condiciones.",
    },
    {
      id: "4",
      title: "¿Cuáles son las marcas o empresas asociadas a Moda link?",
      description:
        "Trabajamos con diversas marcas y empresas mediante programas de afiliados. Al hacer clic en un producto, podrás conocer más sobre la marca y comprar directamente desde su sitio web.",
    },
    {
      id: "5",
      title: "¿Cómo puedo confiar en la calidad de los productos recomendados?",
      description:
        "Nos esforzamos por seleccionar productos de calidad de marcas reputadas. Sin embargo, la garantía de calidad y el servicio postventa dependen del afiliado. Te recomendamos revisar las políticas de cada empresa antes de realizar una compra.",
    },
    {
      id: "6",
      title: "¿Tienen alguna política de devoluciones o reembolsos?",
      description:
        "No gestionamos procesos de devolución ni reembolso, ya que las transacciones se realizan directamente con los afiliados. Asegúrate de revisar las políticas de devolución de la empresa afiliada antes de realizar una compra.",
    },
  ]
  },
};
---

<section class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 md:pt-20 md:pb-10 px-5">
  <div class="flex justify-center items-center flex-col gap-y-3">
    <div
      class="grid items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white p-4 text-color_pink1"
    >
      <svg
        stroke="currentColor"
        fill="currentColor"
        stroke-width="0"
        viewBox="0 0 384 512"
        class="h-8 w-8 rtl:-scale-x-100"
        height="1em"
        width="1em"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        ><path
          d="M202.021 0C122.202 0 70.503 32.703 29.914 91.026c-7.363 10.58-5.093 25.086 5.178 32.874l43.138 32.709c10.373 7.865 25.132 6.026 33.253-4.148 25.049-31.381 43.63-49.449 82.757-49.449 30.764 0 68.816 19.799 68.816 49.631 0 22.552-18.617 34.134-48.993 51.164-35.423 19.86-82.299 44.576-82.299 106.405V320c0 13.255 10.745 24 24 24h72.471c13.255 0 24-10.745 24-24v-5.773c0-42.86 125.268-44.645 125.268-160.627C377.504 66.256 286.902 0 202.021 0zM192 373.459c-38.196 0-69.271 31.075-69.271 69.271 0 38.195 31.075 69.27 69.271 69.27s69.271-31.075 69.271-69.271-31.075-69.27-69.271-69.27z"
        ></path></svg
      >
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-xl md:text-3xl font-fugazOnepx-5 font-fugazOne text-center">
      {faqs[lang].title}
    </h2>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto my-8">
    {
      faqs[lang].questions.map((faq) => (
        <details>
          <summary class="group cursor-pointer grid w-full grid-flow-col items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-start text-lg font-medium transition hover:bg-neutral-100">
            <h3>{faq.title}</h3>
            <svg
              stroke="currentColor"
              fill="currentColor"
              stroke-width="0"
              viewBox="0 0 448 512"
              class="mr-2 h-4 w-4 text-color_pink1 transition group-hover:text-inherit"
              height="1em"
              width="1em"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            >
              <path d="M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="item-details px-4 pt-2 pb-4 max-w-full prose prose-neutral prose-a:no-underline prose-a:text-blue-600 marker:text-xl marker:text-blue-600">
            <p class="sm:text-lg w-10/12">{faq.description}</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      ))
    }
  </div>
</section>
